# Knowledge graph: track the OUTPUTS that help external contributors orient
# (graph.html search UI, graph.json data, GRAPH_REPORT.md god-node summary)
# but ignore intermediate cache + chunk artifacts that are large + regenerable.
# Regenerate via: /graphify .  (Claude Code skill)
graphify-out/cache/
graphify-out/.graphify_*.json
graphify-out/manifest.json
graphify-out/cost.json

# Ad-hoc test reports / debugging output at root (not standard project docs)
/Eject*.md
/Test-Report*.md

# Diagnostic logs and downloads
plans/diagnostics/logs/
plans/diagnostics/downloads/

